name: #MakeItSwift
body:
Find your code here... MakeItSwift with Projects readily available on Github. 
Work with playgrounds and test your code live.
The comments along with the code provide enough information about every snippet present. 
Follow me on Instagram for visuals: www.instagram.com/makeItSwift

Tutorials on YouTube:

Getting Started with Swift Playgrounds in Xcode : https://youtu.be/2UhMa_eawbI
